00:39.213 --> 00:42.477
Stand by for ETA on station.
How copy?

00:42.520 --> 00:44.957
[Nix] Good copy, Highroller.
Evac on the way.

00:46.133 --> 00:49.266
[radio chatter]

00:49.310 --> 00:51.138
[Shepherd] Silver, this
is Shepherd requesting

00:51.181 --> 00:52.356
