-For his protection.

01:28.175 --> 01:30.307
Yeah, for babies.

01:30.351 --> 01:35.573
[radio chatter]

01:35.616 --> 01:38.750
[vehicle rumbling]

01:38.794 --> 01:43.015
[townspeople chatter]

01:43.059 --> 01:45.453
[radio chatter continues]

01:51.589 --> 01:53.025
