03:01.442 --> 03:02.660
It'’s just a feeling.

03:04.227 --> 03:06.795
I pulled it three weeks ago.

03:06.838 --> 03:09.014
-And?
-And what?

03:09.058 --> 03:11.147
-Do you feel any different?
-No.

03:15.586 --> 03:17.675
I watch programs sometimes.

03:17.719 --> 03:19.677
Programs?

03:19.721 --> 03:21.462
Like, about animals and stuff.

03:21.505 --> 03:23.072
Oh.

03:23.115 --> 03:26.118
-Don'’t do that.
-Wait, hold on.

03:27.555 --> 03:29.644
You see that?
Call it in.

03:29.687 --> 03:31.167
It'’s a flash.

03:31.211 --> 03:32.603
-A flicker.
-[tense music]

03:32.647 --> 03:34.736
You want me to
