03:42.439 --> 03:44.528
Plasma. You understand?

03:44.572 --> 03:47.662
You, your people, all this,
turned into glass.

03:49.620 --> 03:50.795
Get that translator down here.

03:50.839 --> 03:52.667
-Sir.
-I understand you.

03:52.710 --> 03:54.408
Good. That'’s great,
