04:33.316 --> 04:36.450
Sir, still no
contact with Bravo.

04:36.493 --> 04:38.147
You'’ll excuse me.

04:40.628 --> 04:43.674
-Not everything has a soul.
-[crowd chattering]

04:43.718 --> 04:46.590
