04:46.634 --> 04:49.898
Some places have souls,
like this one.

04:49.941 --> 04:51.073
[crowd chattering]

04:51.116 --> 04:53.597
Did you know that?

04:53.641 --> 04:54.772
It'’s true.

04:58.428 --> 04:59.777
He'’s going to think about it.

04:59.821 --> 05:02.476
