06:26.995 --> 06:31.173
-What?
-What?

06:31.216 --> 06:34.698
-[grapple pops]
-[dramatic music]

06:34.742 --> 06:40.051
-[ships rumbling]
-[radio chatter]

06:40.095 --> 06:43.577
[townspeople shouting]

06:50.627 --> 06:52.368
